<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="A" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Anne" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Anne.</orth> 1) Saint A.: <bibl n="shak. shr 1.1.255" default="NO" valid="yes">Shr. I, 1, 255</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. tn 2.3.126" default="NO" valid="yes">Tw. II, 3, 126</bibl>. -- 2) daughter of Roger Earl of March: <bibl n="shak. 2h6 2.2.38" default="NO" valid="yes">H6B II, 2, 38</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 2h6 2.2.38" default="NO" valid="yes">H6B II, 2, 38</bibl> -- 3) daughter of Warwick and wife of Prince Edward and King Richard III: <bibl n="shak. r3 1.2.9" default="NO" valid="yes">R3 I, 2, 9</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. r3 4.2.53" default="NO" valid="yes">IV, 2, 53</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. r3 4.3.39" default="NO" valid="yes">3, 39</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. r3 5.3.159" default="NO" valid="yes">V, 3, 159</bibl>. -- 4) A. Bullen, afterwards wife of Henry VIII: <bibl n="shak. h8 3.2.36" default="NO" valid="yes">H8 III, 2, 36</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. h8 3.2.36" default="NO" valid="yes">H8 III, 2, 36</bibl> <bibl n="shak. h8 3.2.36" default="NO" valid="yes">H8 III, 2, 36</bibl> <bibl n="shak. h8 4.1.3" default="NO" valid="yes">IV, 1, 3</bibl>. -- 5) Anne Page: <bibl n="shak. wiv 1.1.45" default="NO" valid="yes">Wiv. I, 1, 45</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. wiv 1.4.33" default="NO" valid="yes">4, 33</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. wiv 2.1.168" default="NO" valid="yes">II, 1, 168</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. wiv 3.4.14" default="NO" valid="yes">III, 4, 14</bibl>. 71 etc.
